Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.51,0:22:26.70,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伴隨著結尾即開始的詠嘆調
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.70,0:22:31.36,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高舉白旗的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.88,0:22:37.12,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在逃獄後的歡呼聲中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.12,0:22:41.31,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被強行拷上了手銬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.75,0:22:47.19,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看吧 愚昧的棋子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.19,0:22:52.24,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這定罪的把戲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.31,0:22:54.97,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奇異的獨角戲舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:22:57.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用你的眼睛看著 競爭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:02.74,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}遺落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.67,0:23:02.74,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欺騙吧 Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.74,0:23:05.33,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多線並行的發展
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.33,0:23:08.14,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}撥開人群
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.14,0:23:10.85,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呼喊著 這是我正義的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.85,0:23:13.23,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}許下你的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.23,0:23:15.84,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}值得讚美的驚恐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.84,0:23:18.54,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唯獨拒絕喪失
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.54,0:23:23.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}指引我吧 Close Enough
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.60,0:23:26.24,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}過於艷麗的忌日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.29,0:23:28.41,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}帶有偏見的分類
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.41,0:23:30.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要相信沒有故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.60,0:23:32.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道你準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.67,0:23:34.52,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 我們已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.52,0:23:36.53,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人人都愛著絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.53,0:23:39.94,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會滿懷悲傷地離去
